title: Bright one-bedroom with deck!
app_fee: $40 application fee per person over the age of 18
posting_body: Available September 1:   Harbor Town Apartments is currently offering bright, spacious, 1-bedroom units in an updated mid-century building.
Excellent Capitol Hill neighborhood with close proximity to both downtown and Madison Park.
The property is close to universities, retail, groceries (including Trader Joe’s and Safeway) and public transportation.
Common area laundry room located on-site.
Please inquire as to availability of additional parking and storage.
TO VIEW, please call/ text Kurt at
$90 per month Utility Fee covers water/sewer/garbage
Harbortown is a No Smoking/ No Pet property
*Photos might not be of exact unit available but do represent the general look of units at this property.
